data.description: Welcome to 412 North Dr, a charming house located in the peaceful town of Lebec, California. This beautiful property offers a comfortable and modern living space for you and your loved ones. With a total of 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this house provides ample space for a growing family or those seeking extra room for guests. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the well-designed layout that maximizes natural light and open spaces. The livable area of 1600 sqft. offers plenty of room to relax, entertain, or simply enjoy time with family and friends. The bedrooms are spacious and cozy, providing a peaceful retreat at the end of each day. The bathrooms are thoughtfully designed with modern fixtures and comfortable amenities, ensuring your daily routines are a breeze. Situated on the second floor, this house offers lovely views and a sense of tranquility. Built in 2006, the property has been well-maintained and boasts a contemporary design that perfectly blends with its surroundings. Located in a quiet neighborhood with 4,792 sqft. that this home sits on, it is an ideal place for those seeking a peaceful and serene environment. The address is highly desirable, ensuring convenience to nearby restaurants, schools, shopping at the nearby outlets and very close access to the freeway. The property is located in a perfect place to make this house your forever home. Don't miss this opportunity to come view, at an incredible price of $390,000.   Contact for more information or to schedule a private viewing. This house is waiting to welcome you home!
